# Components

This project uses React components organized in the `/src/components` directory. 

## Key Components

### Layout Components
- [HeroSection.tsx](mdc:src/components/HeroSection.tsx) - Hero section at the top of the portfolio
- [AboutSection.tsx](mdc:src/components/AboutSection.tsx) - About section with personal information
- [Footer.tsx](mdc:src/components/Footer.tsx) - Site footer with links and copyright information
- [SupportSection.tsx](mdc:src/components/SupportSection.tsx) - Support or contact section

### Project Components
- [ProjectsCarousel.tsx](mdc:src/components/ProjectsCarousel.tsx) - Carousel showing portfolio projects
- [ProjectCard.tsx](mdc:src/components/ProjectCard.tsx) - Individual project card

### UI Components
- [LanguageSwitcher.tsx](mdc:src/components/LanguageSwitcher.tsx) - Component for switching language
- [ThemeToggle.tsx](mdc:src/components/ThemeToggle.tsx) - Dark/light mode toggle
- [SocialLinks.tsx](mdc:src/components/SocialLinks.tsx) - Social media links
- [BeappCTA.tsx](mdc:src/components/BeappCTA.tsx) - Call-to-action component

### SEO Components
- [SEO.tsx](mdc:src/components/SEO.tsx) - SEO optimization component using React Helmet
